OL,6,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report as
OL,7,Fcovert video footage is shown to
OL,8,Fjurors in the Christine Rawle murder
OL,9,Ftrial
OL,11,FA couple at the centre of a murder
OL,12,Ftrial called the police on each other
OL,13,Fmore than a dozen times over the past
OL,14,F30 years, complaining of physical
OL,15,Fviolence, theft and criminal damage.
OL,17,FChristine Rawle, 70, is on trial for
OL,18,Fthe alleged murder of Ian Rawle at
OL,19,Ftheir north Devon home.
