OL,6,FJurors at Exeter Crown Court, where
OL,7,FMrs Rawle is on trial for allegedly
OL,8,Fmurdering Mr Rawle, heard an extensive
OL,9,Flist of the couple's police complaints
OL,10,Fagainst each other, dating back to
OL,11,F1992.
OL,13,FIt was also revealed that Ian Rawle
OL,14,Fonce had his shotgun certificate
OL,15,Frevoked by the police, who said they
OL,16,Fwere concerned he was "easily moved to
OL,17,Fanger" and posed a "danger to public
OL,18,Fsafety".
