OL,6,F"He had a set of heavy garden gloves,"
OL,7,Fhe said.
OL,9,F"I was wearing shorts and a T-shirt.
OL,10,FHe threw the ashtray directly at me
OL,11,Fand it struck me in the leg. It left
OL,12,Fme with a severe circular burn on my
OL,13,Fleg. I was crying.
OL,15,F"He played it down and said he didn't
OL,16,Fmean it in a malicious way, but he
OL,17,Fabsolutely did. It wasn't an accident."
