OL,6,FHe said his mother tried to protect
OL,7,Fhim and a fight broke out. Tom told
OL,8,Fthe court Ian Rawle punched his mother
OL,9,F"in the side of the face."
OL,11,FHe described other incidents in which
OL,12,FIan Rawle hit his mother with a riding
OL,13,Fcrop and "split her face open", and
OL,14,F"kicked her with steel-capped boots
OL,15,Fon".
OL,17,F'If timings were off with meal times,
OL,18,Fthat could cause arguments," Tom Rawle
OL,19,Fsaid.
