OL,3,CMurder trial couple 'called the police
OL,4,Con each other in 30-year period'
OL,6,F"Dad coming home from work, depending
OL,7,Fon what kind of day he'd had, that
OL,8,Fcould cause arguments. If mum hadn't
OL,9,Fdone duties around the house, that
OL,10,Fcould cause arguments.
OL,12,F"He thought I was underachieving and
OL,13,Fthat I wasn't putting enough effort
OL,14,Finto life in the way he would have
OL,15,Fpreferred."
OL,17,FChristine Rawle denies murder and the
OL,18,Ftrial continues.
